2024/06/Glasto@20000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/glastonbury-2024">2024 年格拉斯顿伯</a>里音乐节的大门于昨天（6 月 27 日）开放，现场出售的商品随处可见。</p><ul><li><strong>了解更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-line-up-set-times-stage-splits-3749871">格拉斯顿伯里音乐节 2024：查看舞台时间和完整阵容</a></strong></li></ul><p>舞台之间的各种商品摊位已经开放，沃西农场准备在今天下午晚些时候开始其第一轮表演。</p><p>除了一年一度的节日 T 恤和连帽衫设计（背面有整个钞票）之外，大部分商品都以头条新闻<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sza">SZA</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dua-lipa">Dua Lipa</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shania-twain">仙妮亚·唐恩（Shania Twain）</a>为中心，他们将填补令人垂涎的传奇位置，以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/james">詹姆斯</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-national">国家报</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-last-dinner-party">最后的晚宴</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fontaines-d-c">Fontaines DC</a>等。</p><p>为 Dua Lipa 提供了两件 T 恤和一件长袖上衣。每件 T 恤都印有这位流行歌星的照片，背面写着“激进乐观主义夏季‘24 巡演’”。长袖为黑色，背面印有她的头像以及她最近的欧洲巡演日期列表。 </p><figure id="attachment_3768971" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3768971" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3768971" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Glasto-Merch5@2000x1270.jpg" alt="2024 年格拉斯顿伯里商品" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Glasto-Merch5@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Glasto-Merch5@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Glasto-Merch5@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Glasto-Merch5@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Glasto-Merch5@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Glasto-Merch5@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3768971" class="wp-caption-text">格拉斯顿伯里商品 2024。图片来源：NME</figcaption></figure><p> Twain 有四种 T 恤设计可供选择，其中一款印有她最近最热门专辑的插图。正面显示她穿着豹纹，并写着“亲爱的，我回来了”；它还写着“Giddy Up Glasto！”在背面。</p><p>另外还有两款白色 T 恤设计——每一款都向她最热门的歌曲致敬——还有一款淡粉色 T 恤，展示了这位歌手戴着粉色牛仔帽蹲在迪斯科舞厅前的样子。</p><p> Fontaines DC 提供两件黑色 T 恤，展示他们的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fontaines-d-c-share-pummelling-new-single-starburster-and-announce-new-album-romance-3619061">“Romance”专辑</a>艺术作品。 SZA 提供了一件白色 T 恤和一件黑色连帽衫，每件都展示了各种昆虫，而 James 则提供了一件白色长袖和一件灰色连帽衫。</p><p> T恤的售价大致在30英镑左右，连帽衫的售价在70英镑左右。查看下面提供的更多内容。 </p><figure id="attachment_3768972" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3768972" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3768972" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Glasto-Merch6@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Glasto-Merch6@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Glasto-Merch6@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Glasto-Merch6@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Glasto-Merch6@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Glasto-Merch6@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Glasto-Merch6@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3768972" class="wp-caption-text">格拉斯顿伯里商品 2024。图片来源：NME </figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_3768973" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3768973" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3768973" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Glasto-Merch2@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Glasto-Merch2@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Glasto